    "causal_summary": "Gate E is the canonical cutover for phase 018. The runtime no longer uses a staged rollout ladder, shadow mode, observation windows, or archived-tier continuity semantics. This phase flips the new path to the only live continuity path immediately, removes rollout-era framing from the active surfaces, and updates the mapped command, agent, skill, and README files so the repo describes the shipped contract honestly.",
